## **Summary Checklist for New Tables**

- [ ] `CREATE SEQUENCE public.<table>_id_seq INCREMENT BY 1`
- [ ] `id bigint DEFAULT nextval('public.<table>_id_seq'::regclass) NOT NULL` and `PRIMARY KEY (id)`
- [ ] `tenant_id` (if tenant-scoped)
- [ ] `created_at` / `updated_at` where applicable
- [ ] Java entity with unique `@SequenceGenerator` matching sequence name
- [ ] `allocationSize = 1` on all application entities
- [ ] Entry in `sync_all_table_sequences.sql` (or regenerate via mosc-temp generator script)
